qas.question: Parties to a treaty may disagree over a desire to create an obligation under what?
Discussions between what two countries have been influence by one party's desire to create an obligation under international law?

answers.text: North Korea and the United States

qas.question: Discussion between North Korea and the United States have been influenced by one party's desire to create obligations under international law with respect to what two topics?
North Korea and the United States have been characterized by a disagreement over one parties desire to create what with respect to security guarantees and nuclear proliferation?

answers.text: to create an obligation under international law
